# Module qlmaas

This module *qlmaas* is the client *QLM as a Service*. This module extends
[myQLM](https://pypi.org/project/myqlm/) to submit Quantum jobs to a QLM appliance.

## Prerequisites
This version of myQLM Power Access (a.k.a. QLMaaS) works on both Windows, macOS and Linux for different versions of Python 3. Please look at the [compatibility matrix](https://myqlm.github.io/myqlm_specific/install.html#compatibility-matrix) to ensure myQLM Power Access is installable on your computer.

This module can be installed by typing the following command:

```
pip install qlmaas
```
